                            <div class="img-wrapper">

                                        <img src="/media/1028/11_hr.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=255&amp;height=164&amp;rnd=131818564500000000" width="255" height="164" alt="11_HR.jpg" />

                                    <a href="/about-us/" class="arrow"></a>
                            </div>

                            <p>Melrose buys good manufacturing businesses with strong fundamentals whose performance can be improved. Melrose finances its acquisitions using a low level of leverage, improves the businesses by a mixture of investment and changed management focus, sells them and returns the proceeds to shareholders</p>

